# get_irida_sample_by_name
# gets a single sample by name within a project
# uses undocumented GET /api/projects/{id}/samples/bySampleName?sampleName= endpoint
# endpoint issues a 302 redirect to /api/samples/{id} - requires --location
# PROJECT_ID is used for tab completion and the API call
# SAMPLE_NAME is an exact match - partial names will return 404
#
# example: get_irida_sample_by_name [TAB once for project id] 67:Ecoli 2016-01-4169-1-2-1-1
